<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/756859-can-someone-please-explain-the-twist-at">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Can someone please explain the twist at the end involving Maya/Inara and Sophia? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
