<div id="review_2478937711" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2478937711" />
    <a title="Felicia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13169794-felicia"><img alt="Felicia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1464034900p2/13169794.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2478937711?book_show_action=true">Aug 25, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Felicia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Felicia" href="/user/show/13169794-felicia">Felicia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2478937711" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3383768389360889872">This book is dark with a capital DISTURBING...my favorite kind.<br/><br/>Favorite Quote:<br/>“Some people stay broken. Some pick up the pieces and put them back together with all the sharp edges showing.”<br/><br/>I am now a Dot Hutchinson fan. The imagery she is able to create with words is beyond reproach. Highly recommend for those that enjoy a good mind-fuck.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


